    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was taken in New York, where they live in New York City.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is a photograph of my new-found relatives that originate-- they came from Poland, but they live now in Philadelphia, that I wasn't aware of.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my cousin, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Ida ?] Jarvis invited me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They make every year a family reunion.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's called the [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Goodstein ?] Family Reunion.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in this picture, I found, all of a sudden, from not having Canada relatives, all those relatives.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we try every year on Thanksgiving to get together.",
